        "next_operation": "2024-07-14T15:00:00+05:30"
      },
      "farmer_advisory": [
        "Do NOT enter fields when aerial spraying is announced — maintain 48-hour buffer period",
        "Report locust sightings immediately to Gram Sevak or call 1800-180-1551",
        "Use noise (drums, firecrackers, tin banging) at dawn/dusk when locusts are roosting to drive them away",
        "Create smoke barriers on windward side of fields using dried dung, husk, or wood",
        "All water sources must be covered before spraying operations begin",
        "Harvest mature crops immediately if swarm approach is confirmed within 48 hours"
